        <h1>Eterna Essenza Health Education</h1>
        <p>We aim to provide knowledge that you can use every day, wherever you are – whether you're traveling or at home. It’s essential to listen to your body, recognize when it is in need, and take action to help it.</p>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>Available Courses</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <h3>Breast Self-Examination, Prevention, and Self-Help</h3>
                <p>Understanding the importance of regular screening programs and how to recognize warning signs. This course will help you learn the steps for self-examination and the importance of early detection.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Principles of Lymphatic Drainage and Self-Massage</h3>
                <p>Learn the basics of lymphatic drainage techniques and self-massage that promote overall health and well-being.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Menstrual Cycle and Hormones: Nutrition and Skin Care According to Your Cycle</h3>
                <p>Make the difference between your menstrual cycle and the bleeding period within it. We will explore ovulation, pre- and post-ovulation phases, and how to adjust nutrition accordingly to optimize your health throughout the cycle.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Breastfeeding and Breast Care</h3>
                <p>This course includes practical techniques and exercises on models, so you can be fully prepared to care for yourself and your baby.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>The Science of Sex: Problems, Questions, and Solutions</h3>
                <p>In this course, we’ll explore the science of sex, address common questions, and offer solutions to frequent problems.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Support for Assisted Reproductive Technology (ART) Preparation</h3>
                <p>This course provides valuable information and support for those preparing for ART procedures like IVF and other fertility treatments.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Wound Dressing and Care Course</h3>
                <p>Learn the techniques for dressing and caring for wounds, an essential skill for personal care or for assisting others in need.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Skin and Hair Care Related to Menstrual Cycle</h3>
                <p>Discover how your menstrual cycle affects your skin and hair and learn how to adjust your skincare and hair care routine accordingly.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Everything You Need to Know About Childbirth</h3>
                <p>This course covers everything you need to know about childbirth, from early preparation to the delivery process, ensuring you're fully informed and ready for the big day.</p>
            </li>
